pageProduct.name: Thompson's Biotin 150mcg 100 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's Biotin 150mcg helps support the metabolism of carbohydrates, fats and proteins and helps maintain the metabolism of macronutrients.

Size: 100tabs

KEY FEATURES

• Helps support the metabolism of carbohydrates, fats and proteins.
• Helps maintain the metabolism of macronutrients.
• Vegetarian/Vegan friendly.

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Eacht tablet contains:
Biotin (Vitamin H) 150mcg

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
